ent are SSH2_POLL* flags bitwise ORed together.      Each subarray will be populated with an <span class="literal">'revents'</span> element on return,      whose values are SSH2_POLL* flags bitwise ORed together of the events that occurred.     </p>    </dd>          <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">timeout</span></dt>    <dd>     <p class="para">      The timeout in seconds.     </p>    </dd>     </dl> </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.ssh2-poll-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns the number of descriptors which returned non-zero revents.  </p> </div></div>
