;</span></span></blockquote></div>    </div>   </div>      </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ssh2-sftp-readlink-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link readlink()} - 返回符号连接指向的目标</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link ssh2_sftp_symlink()} - Create a symlink</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
